Package author: Andrei Salnikov

Brief description:
==================

This package contains files necessary to build online-to-offline (o2o) 
translator for LUSI data. 

Detailed description:
=====================

The main application in this package is o2o-translator. It reads online-
produced XTC file and optionally EPICS data file. It writes the output
file in the offline format (nexus/hdf5).  

